You should scold them for being so ridiculous.

35
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:28,580
Seoul is miles away.

36
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:30,490
Is America a joke?

37
00:02:30,490 --> 00:02:32,680
You should be angry at them.

38
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,290
Has...

39
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:37,020
Has everyone gone crazy?

40
00:02:37,020 --> 00:02:38,600
I'll...

41
00:02:39,230 --> 00:02:41,320
I'll talk to her.

42
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:44,660
You should head down, too.

43
00:02:45,490 --> 00:02:47,230
Hae Joon.

44
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:05,420
San Ha will help her understand.

45
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:08,660
She listens to San Ha.

46
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:10,170
Yes.

47
00:03:10,170 --> 00:03:12,120
 How could you make that decision alone? 

48
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:14,370
That's why I returned to discuss this in person.

49
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:16,050
Isn't it more like notifying us?

50
00:03:16,050 --> 00:03:18,720
You should've asked us before making a decision.

51
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:21,100
That's what families do.

52
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:25,630
You didn't consider asking us, did you?

53
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:28,360
Since you have a real family somewhere else.

54
00:03:29,730 --> 00:03:31,890
Since we aren't your real family.

55
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,430
Why are you bringing that up again?

56
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:37,590
You didn't even consider asking us since we aren't your real family.

57
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:39,960
You don't care about us in the slightest right now.

58
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:43,910
You didn't even think about how my dad or I would feel

59
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:46,350
if you left, did you?

60
00:03:46,350 --> 00:03:49,670
You only thought about your younger sister and mom, right?

61
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:02,530
Can't I?

62
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:11,490
Is something wrong with me taking care of my younger sister and mom?

63
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:15,810
Kang Hae Joon and I will be 20 years old next year.

64
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:19,200
Naturally, our responsibilities will grow.

65
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:26,080
All right.

66
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:30,880
So you're saying we aren't part of your responsibilities.

67
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,620
I understood it all well.

68
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:48,740
What's the matter? What's the matter?

69
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:54,510
Hey, Joo Won. Open the door. Aren't you eating?

70
